embeddableConfig.content:
Microsoft Foundry API Management

This dashboard focuses on logs and metrics generated by the Microsoft Foundry service when accessed via the API Management service only. 
APIM adds an extra layer of API-level monitoring, enabling full control over logging and monitoring for every request routed through the gateway. 

This dashboard contains:

- Request rate
- Error rate
- Model usage
- Latency
- LLM prompt input, Response completion
